Class RBNBChannelObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • helpers.RBNBChannelObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RBNBChannelObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a helper class used to store channel information as well as the channel's datapoints and timestamps in an array of XYDataPointObjects
    Author:
    jdk85
